Package: psiplot
Title: Generate plots of PSI values generated by vast-tools
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: "Kevin Ha <k.ha@mail.utoronto.ca> [aut, cre]"
Description: Provides functions to create plots of PSI values of
    alternatively-spliced exons. Requires PSI data generated by the program
    vast-tools (https://github.com/vastgroup/vast-tools).
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.1)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/kcha/psiplot
BugReports: https://github.com/kcha/psiplot/issues
Imports:
    ggplot2 (>= 1.0.0),
    reshape2 (>= 1.4)
Suggests:
    testthat
